All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, Iterable<Instruction>, Collection<Instruction>, List<Instruction>, RandomAccess
public class InstructionBlock
extends Stack<Instruction>

The Class InstructionBlock. Stack to represent an instruction block. An instruction block is a list of instructions starting with an instruction with a jump label. The fist Instruction pushed to the block will get the instruction block label assigned to it.
